<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Experiment 6 | Docker</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h1 { color: #2496ed; } /* Docker Blue */
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Experiment 6: Success!</h1>
        <p>This application is running inside a <strong>Docker Container</strong>.</p>
        <p>Managed via <strong>WSL2</strong>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
